description: IDeliverable.Slides is module for the Orchard CMS that allows editors to easily add slideshows to their websites. Each slide is a layout, allowing complete visual control and content flexibility, and can be added either statically or dynamically based on projections and lists. Out of the box, slideshows can be rendered using either Bootstrap Carousel, Cycle2 or jCarousel. Developers can easily extend this list by writing their own plugins using an easy-to-use API.
summary: A module for the Orchard CMS that allows editors to easily add slideshows to their websites.
